OL,3,CTerminally ill man 'wasted away in
OL,4,Chome' due to no suitable hire cars
OL,6,FA Jersey woman whose terminally ill
OL,7,Fbrother struggled to get around the
OL,8,Fisland in the final months of his life
OL,9,Fwants hire car companies to offer
OL,10,Faccessible vehicles locally.
OL,12,FAnita Twohig's sibling Simon was
OL,13,Fdiagnosed with inoperable brain cancer
OL,14,Fat the age of 53 and as the condition
OL,15,Fprogressed, he needed to move into a
OL,16,Fcare home and use a wheelchair.
