OL,3,CTerminally ill man 'wasted away in
OL,4,Chome' due to no suitable hire cars
OL,6,FAnita says: "While the home were
OL,7,Fbrilliant, we just wanted him to see
OL,8,Fhis friends at the pub and go out for
OL,9,Fdinner but we couldn't get hold of any
OL,10,Ftransport.
OL,12,F"The care homes have their vehicles
OL,13,Fbut they're for outings of more than
OL,14,Fone person.
OL,16,F"It was awful, he was 53/54 wasting
OL,17,Faway, stuck in a home. We could've
OL,18,Fmade it a lot better had we got him
OL,19,Fout."
