OL,3,CTerminally ill man 'wasted away in
OL,4,Chome' due to no suitable hire cars
OL,6,FITV News has checked with Jersey's
OL,7,Fthree main hire car companies and none
OL,8,Fof them offer wheelchair-accessible
OL,9,Fvehicles.
OL,11,FAnita also tried charities and taxi
OL,12,Ffirms but faced more issues: "Going
OL,13,Fthrough the list, it was always no
OL,14,Favailability or their business had
OL,15,Fbeen closed.
OL,17,F"Simon's not the only one diagnosed
OL,18,Fwith this disease or that needs to be
OL,19,Fin a bigger wheelchair which you can't
OL,20,Fget them out of to sit in a car."
