OL,3,CTerminally ill man 'wasted away in
OL,4,Chome' due to no suitable hire cars
OL,6,FEventually, Anita says she found a
OL,7,Ftaxi driver with an adapted vehicle
OL,8,Fwho could take them but only once
OL,9,Fevery fortnight.
OL,11,FShe explains: "We'd prebook it for
OL,12,FSunday every two weeks and his hours
OL,13,Fwere like 12-3 so if you're going out
OL,14,Fit was a quick lunch and then you'd
OL,15,Fhave to rush back.
OL,17,F"I've got a friend that's involved
OL,18,Fwith the Royal British Legion and they
OL,19,Fhave a disability vehicle which they
OL,20,Foffered to loan to me but by that
OL,21,Ftime, my brother had passed."
