OL,3,CTerminally ill man 'wasted away in
OL,4,Chome' due to no suitable hire cars
OL,6,FAnita would like to see Jersey's
OL,7,Fgovernment support charities and the
OL,8,Fcar rental sector to make the island
OL,9,Fmore accessible.
OL,11,FSean Pontin, Chief Executive Officer
OL,12,Fof Enable Jersey, adds: "I really
OL,13,Fworry that some of those things like
OL,14,Fdisability have gone down the pecking
OL,15,Forder. Then we have to ask ourselves
OL,16,Fwhether disability is really on
OL,17,Fpeople's priority list any more."
