OL,3,CTerminally ill man 'wasted away in
OL,4,Chome' due to no suitable hire cars
OL,6,FIn response, Jersey's Sustainable
OL,7,FEconomic Development Minister, Deputy
OL,8,FKirsten Morel, says: "It is important
OL,9,Fthat we all think about accessibility
OL,10,Fand inclusivity for everyone.
OL,12,F"We are always looking at different
OL,13,Fways to achieve this and I would be
OL,14,Fhappy to discuss this more with
OL,15,Fislanders so we can help make Jersey a
OL,16,Fmore accessible place."
